data.description: **NEW PRICE REDUCTION!** Just in time for the holidays! This beautiful home has an exceptional floor plan complete with 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths. Master Suite features large shower, double vanity with a HUGE walk-in closet!! Kitchen has beautiful wood cabinetry, granite counter tops complete with stainless steel appliances, offers plenty of counter and cabinet space and opens to a large living area, both with a view of the backyard and large covered lanai, great for entertaining! Tile throughout main living areas. Home is equipped with Smart features and sellers are throwing in the large capacity washer and dryer! Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! VERY MOTIVATED SELLERS SO MAKE AN OFFER TODAY!!
